<h4 id="automatic-nightlight">Automatic Nightlight</h4>

<h4 id="schematic-image">Schematic Image</h4>

<h4 id="parts-list">Parts List</h4>

<ul>
  <li>1 10k Resistors</li>
  <li>1 10k Potentiometer</li>
  <li>1 470-500 ohm Resistor</li>
  <li>1 NPN Transistor (2n2222 works nice)</li>
  <li>Protoboard</li>
  <li>1 LDR (Light Dependent Resistor)/Photocell</li>
  <li>An LED of choice color (may need to change the value of R3)</li>
  <li>2 AAA batteries (with lots of tape and</li>
</ul>

