<h3 id="problems">Problems</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Lithium Ion Batteries are expensive as are battery holders. Since I needed to construct the kit on a limited budget I had to use AAA batteries and make my own battery packs using wire and electrical tape.</li>
  <li>Teaching circuit theory and soldering at the same time is hardâ€¦ Next time focus on one of the other.</li>
  <li>Transistors can be tricky to read and set up</li>
  <li>Radioshack is expensive an unreliable.</li>
</ul>
